_School_Color_Cycling_with_HTML5\">show me the code</a>] • This demo is an implementation of a full 8-bit color cycling engine, rendered into an HTML5 Canvas in real-time.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-11T18:31:32.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Canvas</h2><h3>Examples</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://cssdeck.com/labs/full/zeaklousedit\">Circular Rings</a> [<a href=\"http://cssdeck.com/labs/zeaklousedit\">show me the code</a>] • A great example about how to create circular rings using canvas.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-11T18:31:32.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Canvas</h2><h3>Examples</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://cssdeck.com/labs/full/fibrous\">Fibrous Texture</a> [<a href=\"http://cssdeck.com/labs/fibrous\">show me the code</a>] • Simple canvas based animation; draws random lines across the field. Makes an interesting papery pattern that becomes increasingly detailed with each iteration.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-11T18:31:32.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Canvas</h2><h3>Examples</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://cssdeck.com/labs/full/image-nodes\">Image Nodes</a> [<a href=\"http://cssdeck.com/labs/image-nodes\">show me the code</a>] • Interactive nodes built from image data. Use the mouse to play.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-11T18:31:32.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Canvas</h2><h3>Examples</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://cssdeck.com/labs/full/js-metaballs\">JS Metaballs</a> [<a href=\"http://cssdeck.com/labs/js-metaballs\">show me the code</a>] • Experiment for Chrome. Mix of webkit-filter and canvas for a metaballs effect.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-11T18:31:32.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Canvas</h2><h3>Examples</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://codepen.io/ara_node/full/nuJCG/\">Motion Graphic Typeface</a> [<a href=\"http://codepen.io/ara_node/pen/nuJCG\">show me the code</a>] • A example about typeface animation.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-11T18:31:32.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Canvas</h2><h3>Examples</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://gyu.que.jp/jscloth/\">Cloth 3D Effect</a> (Google Chrome strongly recommended) • Thid demo renders a 3d model of Apple iPod with sphere environmental mapping technique.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-11T18:25:23.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Canvas</h2><h3>Examples</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://lab.hakim.se/linjer/\">Linjer</a> • Amazing experiment about nodes effects in addition with cloth and animation effect.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-11T18:25:23.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Canvas</h2><h3>Examples</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://spielzeugz.de/html5/liquid-particles.html\">Liquid Particles</a> • A good example about Liquid Particles.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-11T18:25:23.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Canvas</h2><h3>Examples</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.lucidchart.com/documents/demo\">LucidChart</a> • A complete tool to draw diagrams and other geometric forms, made in canvas.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-11T18:25:23.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Libraries</h2><h3>For other purposes, but still use canvas</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Flipboard/react-canvas\">React Canvas</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Flipboard/react-canvas\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">12.6k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":12643,\"repo\":\"Flipboard/react-canvas\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - High performance <canvas> rendering for React components.</canvas></li>","updatedAt":"2015-06-07T17:42:02.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources<