/li>","updatedAt":"2015-02-04T01:50:37.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Books</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.packtpub.com/web-development/html5-canvas-cookbook\">HTML5 Canvas Cookbook</a> - by Eric Rowell</li>","updatedAt":"2015-02-02T16:00:12.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Websites and Tutorials</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.williammalone.com/articles/create-html5-canvas-javascript-game-character/1/\">Create a game chracter with HTML5 and JavaScript - Part 1</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-01-24T19:41:47.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Websites and Tutorials</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.williammalone.com/articles/create-html5-canvas-javascript-game-character/2/\">Create a game chracter with HTML5 and JavaScript - Part 2</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-01-24T19:41:47.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Websites and Tutorials</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://medium.com/@raphamorim/draw-particles-using-html5-canvas-6151ab214f7a\">Draw Particles using HTML5 Canvas</a> - Shortcut tutorial shows how create simple and colorful particles.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-01-12T15:19:56.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Books</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1430232919/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&#x26;tag=rawkes-20&#x26;linkCode=as2&#x26;camp=1789&#x26;creative=9325&#x26;creativeASIN=1430232919\">Foundation HTML5 Canvas: For Games and Entertainment</a> by Rob Hawkes</li>","updatedAt":"2015-01-08T01:27:24.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Websites and Tutorials</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.html5canvastutorials.com/\">HTML5 Canvas Tutorials</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-01-04T23:32:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Websites and Tutorials</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://billmill.org/static/canvastutorial/\">Breakout</a> - a fantastic tutorial for any canvas programming wannabes, where he runs through the steps needed to create a Breakout clone. The tutorial consists of 12 very clear and concise steps, where you can view a demo of how your project should look so far.</li>","updatedAt":"2014-12-30T15:15:14.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Websites and Tutorials</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://acko.net/blog/js1k-demo-the-making-of/\">Procedural Drawing in Canvas</a> - a tutorial that explains more about how procedural drawing works so that others can also learn the skill and start producing their own patterns.</li>","updatedAt":"2014-12-30T15:15:14.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Websites and Tutorials</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.felinesoft.com/blog/index.php/2010/09/accelerated-game-programming-with-html5-and-canvas/\">Accelerated Game Programming with HTML5 and canvas</a> - this tutorial describes the structure of a typical game class in JavaScript, drawing to the canvas, double buffering, map/tile representation and player movement.</li>","updatedAt":"2014-12-30T15:15:14.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Websites and Tutorials</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://labs.skookum.com/demos/barcampclt_physics/\">Physics for Lazy Game Developers</a> - Provides examples of velocity, acceleration, collisions, rotation and particle effects.</li>","updatedAt":"2014-12-30T15:15:14.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Talks</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Prkyd5n0P7k\">Google I/O 2012 - GRITS: PvP Gaming with HTML, by Colton McAnlis</a></li>","updatedAt":"2014-12-30T01:54:40.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Talks</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_fBRJgH_c1s\">Mobile HTML5 Graphics Performance, by Sam Abadir</a></li>","updatedAt":"2014-12-30T01:54:40.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Talks</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S256vAqGY6c\">The Making of an HTML5 Platform Game, by David Geary</a></li>","updatedAt":"2014-12-30T01:54:40.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Talks</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T8OCEqM7mqU\">High Performance Mobile Web Game Development in HTML5, by Sangmin Shim</a></li>","updatedAt":"2014-12-30T01:54:40.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Talks</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sLt9WeyGVEQ\">HTML5 Canvas Animation with Javascript, by Josh Robertson</a></li>","updatedAt":"2014-12-30T01:54:40.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Books</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://shop.oreilly.com/product/0636920013327.do\">HTML5 Canvas</a> by Steve Fulton, Jeff Fulton - O'Reilly. Updated: <a href=\"http://shop.oreilly.com/product/0636920026266.do\">2nd Edition</a></li>","updatedAt":"2014-12-26T04:37:05.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Books</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/HTML5-Canvas-For-Dummies-Cowan/dp/1118385357\">HTML5 Canvas For Dummies</a> by  Don Cowan</li>","updatedAt":"2014-12-26T04:37:05.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Websites and Tutorials</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://creativejs.com/2011/08/31-days-of-canvas-tutorials/\">31 days of canvas</a></li>","updatedAt":"2014-12-26T01:33:23.000Z"}]},"previous":{"id":"awesomes/github.com/willianjusten/awesome-svg","repo":"willianjusten/awesome-svg"},"next":{"id":"awesomes/github.com/dnbard/awesome-knockout","repo":"dnbard/awesome-knockout"}},"pageContext":{"repo":"raphamorim/awesome-canvas","id":"awesomes/github.com/raphamorim/awesome-canvas","previousId":"awesomes/github.com/willianjusten/awesome-svg","nextId":"awesomes/github.com/dnbard/awesome-knockout"}},"staticQueryHashes":["147714651","228695001","2744905544"]}